import React from 'react' import axios from 'axios' import { useState, useEffect } from 'react' export default function DataShowing() { const[users, setUser]=useState([]) useEffect(()=>{ axios.get('http://localhost:3001/user') .then(users=> setUser(users.data)) .catch(err=>console.log(err)) console.log(users) }, []) return (
{users.map(user=>{ return })}
Id Title Created_by
{user.Id} {user.Created_Date} {user.Created_by}
) }
